# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local-machine recovery tool. Created by `Unlock Git.command` (project root)
# the first time Melanie runs it; cleans up stale .git/*.lock files left
# behind by the Cowork sandbox. NOT project code — local-only, per-machine.
# Full context: Melanie's Context/memory/sandbox_git_lock_avoidance.md.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Unlock Git.command

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Generated SQL from scripts/import-*-csv.py — CSV bulk imports for CIN7 (AU
# sales orders) and Woo AU (Metorik). Regenerated on every run, sizes vary
# with CSV scale (~30 KB for CIN7, ~28 MB for Woo AU). Preserved on failure
# for debugging, otherwise transient. Not source code.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
scripts/.tmp-cin7-import.sql
scripts/.tmp-woo-au-import.sql
